---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Business Solutions — Stillware Ltd"
  description="Custom software and AI solutions built on your infrastructure. You own the code, the data, and the result. No vendor lock-in."
>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="biz-hero">
        <div class="hero-ambient" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <span class="hero-label">Stillware for Business</span>
            <h1>We build it.<br />You own it.</h1>
            <p class="hero-sub">Custom software and AI solutions deployed on your infrastructure. You own every line of code, every model, every pipeline. No vendor lock-in. No recurring platform fees.</p>
            <div class="hero-cta">
                <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary pulse">Start a Conversation</a>
                <a href="/manifesto" class="btn-text">Read Our Manifesto</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- What We Build -->
    <section class="services-section reveal">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header center-text">
                <h2>What We Build</h2>
                <p class="section-sub">From internal tools to AI automation — built to your spec, deployed on your terms.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="services-grid">
                <div class="service-card reveal-up reveal-delay-1">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"/><path d="M15 2v2"/><path d="M15 20v2"/><path d="M2 15h2"/><path d="M2 9h2"/><path d="M20 15h2"/><path d="M20 9h2"/><path d="M9 2v2"/><path d="M9 20v2"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Custom Software Development</h3>
                    <p>Web apps, desktop tools, mobile applications, and internal platforms. Built with modern stacks, delivered with full source code ownership.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card reveal-up reveal-delay-2">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a4 4 0 0 0-4 4c0 2 2 3 2 6h4c0-3 2-4 2-6a4 4 0 0 0-4-4z"/><path d="M10 12h4"/><path d="M10 16h4"/><path d="M10 20h4"/><path d="M12 20v2"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>AI & Automation Solutions</h3>
                    <p>Intelligent workflows, document processing, predictive analytics, and custom AI agents. Deployed on your cloud or on-premise — your data never leaves your control.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card reveal-up reveal-delay-3">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17.5 19H9a7 7 0 1 1 6.71-9h1.79a4.5 4.5 0 1 1 0 9Z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Data & Integration</h3>
                    <p>Connect your existing systems, migrate legacy platforms, and build data pipelines that run on your infrastructure — not ours.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Stillware Difference -->
    <section class="difference-section reveal">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header center-text">
                <h2>The Stillware Difference</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="difference-grid">
                <div class="diff-card">
                    <span class="diff-number">01</span>
                    <h3>You Own the Code</h3>
                    <p>Every line of source code is yours. Full repository access from day one. No proprietary lock-in, no licensing traps.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="diff-card">
                    <span class="diff-number">02</span>
                    <h3>Your Infrastructure</h3>
                    <p>We deploy on your cloud, your servers, your terms. We never host your data or your application on Stillware infrastructure.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="diff-card">
                    <span class="diff-number">03</span>
                    <h3>No Recurring Fees</h3>
                    <p>Project-based pricing. You pay for the build, not a monthly platform fee. Ongoing support is available but never mandatory.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="diff-card">
                    <span class="diff-number">04</span>
                    <h3>Walk Away Anytime</h3>
                    <p>If we part ways, everything keeps running. Your software has no dependency on Stillware. That's the whole point.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How We Work -->
    <section class="process-section reveal">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header center-text">
                <h2>How We Work</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="process-steps">
                <div class="process-step reveal-up reveal-delay-1">
                    <div class="step-marker">1</div>
                    <h3>Discovery Call</h3>
                    <p>30-minute conversation to understand your problem, your constraints, and whether we're the right fit.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="process-connector"></div>
                <div class="process-step reveal-up reveal-delay-2">
                    <div class="step-marker">2</div>
                    <h3>Scoping & Proposal</h3>
                    <p>We define the deliverables, timeline, and a fixed project price. No surprises, no hourly billing ambiguity.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="process-connector"></div>
                <div class="process-step reveal-up reveal-delay-3">
                    <div class="step-marker">3</div>
                    <h3>Build & Ship</h3>
                    <p>Weekly updates, working demos, and direct access to the development team. You see progress, not just status reports.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="process-connector"></div>
                <div class="process-step reveal-up reveal-delay-4">
                    <div class="step-marker">4</div>
                    <h3>Handover</h3>
                    <p>Full source code, documentation, deployment guide, and knowledge transfer. The project is yours — completely.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact -->
    <section class="contact-section" id="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="contact-grid">
                <div class="contact-text">
                    <h2>Let's Build Something.</h2>
                    <p>Tell us what you're working on. We'll get back to you within 24 hours with an honest assessment of whether we can help.</p>
                    <div class="contact-details">
                        <p class="contact-email">business@stillwareltd.com</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-form-wrap">
                    <form name="business-inquiry" method="POST" data-netlify="true" action="/success" class="contact-form">
                        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="business-inquiry" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Business Inquiry" />
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="biz-name">Your Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="biz-name" name="name" required />
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="biz-email">Work Email</label>
                            <input type="email" id="biz-email" name="email" required />
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="biz-company">Company</label>
                            <input type="text" id="biz-company" name="company" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="biz-message">What are you looking to build?</label>
                            <textarea id="biz-message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Send Inquiry</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    /* Hero */
    .biz-hero {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 12rem 0 8rem;
        text-align: center;
        background:
            radial-gradient(ellipse 900px 700px at 50% 40%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.07) 0%, transparent 70%),
            var(--gradient-obsidian);
    }

    .hero-ambient {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 0;
    }

    .hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .hero-label {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 100px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
        color: #60A5FA;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 4rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .hero-sub {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        max-width: 620px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .hero-cta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .hero-cta .btn-text {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        text-decoration-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }

    .hero-cta .btn-text:hover {
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration-color: #ffffff;
    }

    /* Services */
    .services-section {
        padding: 6rem 0;
        background: var(--color-surface);
    }

    .section-sub {
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        max-width: 550px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .services-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .service-card {
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        transition: all 0.4s var(--transition-premium);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-premium);
    }

    .service-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-6px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08);
        border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
    }

    .service-icon {
        width: 56px;
        height: 56px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EFF6FF, #DBEAFE);
        border-radius: 14px;
        color: var(--color-primary);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .service-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .service-card p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* Difference */
    .difference-section {
        padding: 6rem 0;
    }

    .difference-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 3rem auto 0;
    }

    .diff-card {
        padding: 2rem;
        background: var(--color-surface);
        border-radius: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .diff-number {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--color-primary);
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 100px;
    }

    .diff-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .diff-card p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Process */
    .process-section {
        padding: 6rem 0;
        background: var(--color-surface);
    }

    .process-steps {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 0;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 3rem auto 0;
        padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .process-step {
        text-align: center;
        flex: 1;
        padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .step-marker {
        width: 48px;
        height: 48px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
        background: var(--color-primary);
        color: #ffffff;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .process-step h3 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .process-step p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .process-connector {
        width: 40px;
        height: 2px;
        background: var(--color-border);
        margin-top: 24px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* Contact */
    .contact-section {
        padding: 6rem 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 50%, #0F172A 100%);
    }

    .contact-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 4rem;
        align-items: start;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .contact-text h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .contact-text p {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .contact-details {
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .contact-email {
        color: #60A5FA !important;
        font-size: 1.1rem !important;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .contact-form {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .form-group {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.4rem;
    }

    .form-group label {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group textarea {
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        outline: none;
        transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus {
        border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    }

    .form-group input::placeholder,
    .form-group textarea::placeholder {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }

    .form-group textarea {
        resize: vertical;
        min-height: 100px;
    }

    .contact-form .btn-primary {
        align-self: flex-start;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .biz-hero { padding: 10rem 0 6rem; }
        .hero-content h1 { font-size: 2.75rem; }
        .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .difference-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .process-steps { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
        .process-connector { width: 2px; height: 24px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    }
</style>
